  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators hypothesize that incorporation of a colorimetric scale on urine collection
      bags to estimate degree of hematuria would allow better characterization of urine by
      healthcare staff thus leading to improved patient care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
